| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1238 — Recovery Inhibition (payoutsking)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4e922647-e8ff-5a0f-8b4d-581402fabcc2"
